@*
    _NavQuickActions.cshtml — Sprint 11.5 PR #2 / Nav-1.
    ADR-017 §D5 — Quick Actions verb tray.

    Five highest-frequency cross-cutting verbs. Each opens a focused
    create-flow page (not a table). Membership is intentionally cross-
    role: any user can hit any of these without first navigating to a
    role-specific Control Center.

    The slot will house future verbs (Reconcile, Reopen, Reassign) as
    sprints add them — "Quick Actions" is the label rather than "Create"
    because not every future verb is a creation.
*@

<div class="nav-section-label">QUICK ACTIONS</div>

